A lazy function declared in 'beat_schedule' and called before sending to worker.

Example:

    beat_schedule = {
        'test-every-5-minutes': {
            'task': 'test',
            'schedule': 300,
            'kwargs': {
                "current": BeatCallBack(datetime.datetime.now)
            }
        }
    }

